  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Story</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One day, the hero suddenly becomes irresistible!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405490/extras/eb3dce4ff0a52d0bc057d1646e2eede6.avif?t=1751115179\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405490/extras_big/eb3dce4ff0a52d0bc057d1646e2eede6.avif?t=1751115179 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, there is only one girl he has his heart set on!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Can he overcome all kinds of love confessions and tell his feelings to that girl?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Game Flow</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is mainly composed of story parts and battle parts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405490/extras/441a84886bcfa7bfc45573b008eba64d.avif?t=1751115179\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405490/extras_big/441a84886bcfa7bfc45573b008eba64d.avif?t=1751115179 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the battle part, in addition to the various mob heroines that rush in in large numbers, about 10 mid-boss heroines and the boss heroines of each stage,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >very attractive heroines will attack in turn.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405490/extras/e48a28f4079d8eadc67fa2522dd4c245.avif?t=1751115179\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405490/extras_big/e48a28f4079d8eadc67fa2522dd4c245.avif?t=1751115179 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405490/extras/cbe14e44cc9b1858ab3e4e5f34cd30bb.avif?t=1751115179\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405490/extras_big/cbe14e44cc9b1858ab3e4e5f34cd30bb.avif?t=1751115179 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405490/extras/a04d0cf45033d66667cb3ebf00016d76.avif?t=1751115179\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405490/extras_big/a04d0cf45033d66667cb3ebf00016d76.avif?t=1751115179 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How to play</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use all your skills to turn down the girls at school who are trying to confess their love to you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405490/extras/cdf645bd39e63ea37f37507878ae6230.avif?t=1751115179\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405490/extras_big/cdf645bd39e63ea37f37507878ae6230.avif?t=1751115179 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's heartbreaking to turn down a girl's confession...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But it's that pain that will help you level up!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get new skills every time you level up!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405490/extras/25fb592eea1970a7bacd3d5e5e168d03.avif?t=1751115179\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405490/extras_big/25fb592eea1970a7bacd3d5e5e168d03.avif?t=1751115179 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Occasionally, girls will drop gift boxes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perhaps it's something they prepared for the main character.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I feel a bit sorry, but I'll accept it without hesitation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405490/extras/2cc30325f22138d7587b63b02599c099.avif?t=1751115179\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405490/extras_big/2cc30325f22138d7587b63b02599c099.avif?t=1751115179 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Overcome the numerous mob heroines and mid-boss heroines,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and at the end of the stage, the boss heroine awaits you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you can withstand her onslaught and reject her confession, you've cleared the game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405490/extras/847639267949a2d6c49ed0bf96725d09.avif?t=1751115179\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3405490/extras_big/847639267949a2d6c49ed0bf96725d09.avif?t=1751115179 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆Genre</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Van-saba-like 2D action & beautiful girl novel</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆Choices</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are no choices in the novel part.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*There are special events that occur depending on whether you win or lose in some action parts</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆Play Time</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >About 4 hours</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >[Game Streaming]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Streaming and commentary are allowed for this game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Please feel free to share your thoughts on playing the game, your favorite characters,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >your thoughts on the ending, and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*We would appreciate it if you could include the game title or a link to Steam, etc. in the description section.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
